cameraplus (0.0.8-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Reworked preview animation
  * Fixed reboot banner not showing up (Fix by SteveYoungs).
  * Improved start up time a bit
  * Added an option to disable preview for captured images and recorded videos
  * Added support for strftime() formatting to creator name text

 -- Mohammed Sameer <msameer@foolab.org>  Sun, 15 Sep 2013 03:55:00 +0300

cameraplus (0.0.7-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Hopefully prevent GPS from running all the time.
  * Prevent screen dimming while playing a video in post capture
  * Standby screen does not prevent going to settings or post capture anymore
  * Delay capturing via proximity sensor by half a second to prevent accidental trigger.
  * Fix a crash when capturing an image and immediately closing camera.
  * Notify user to reboot the phone after installation.
  * Optimize loading DCIM folder contents when navigating to post capture view

 -- Mohammed Sameer <msameer@foolab.org>  Sun, 08 Sep 2013 20:55:05 +0300

cameraplus (0.0.6-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Make sure we don't play camera sounds in silent profile
  * Don't reuse a file name if a file gets deleted
  * Make capture buttons always visible
  * Added an option to use proximity sensor as a shutter button
  * Reworked toolbar animation to use opacity
  * Don't try to capture if zoom gets pressed and we are in settings or post capture
  * Reworked post capture to get rid of tracker dependency
  * Dropped add to/remove from favorites

 -- Mohammed Sameer <msameer@foolab.org>  Sat, 24 Aug 2013 12:34:21 +0300

